# Shortcuts

## Create / Delete
Create window	C-a c
Name window	C-a ,
Kill window	C-a x
Horiz. pane	C-a - (dash)
Vert. pane	C-a _ (vertical)

## Navigation
Previous window	C-a C-h
Next window	C-a C-l

Previous pane	C-a h
Next pane	C-a l
Swap panes	C-a <, C-a >

## Resizing panes
Left		C-a H
Right		C-a L
Up		C-a J
Down		C-a K

## Misc.
Copy mode	C-a Enter
Copy w/ mouse   Hold shift, highlight and copy
Clipboard copy  (in Copy mode) v -> (vi movement keys) -> y -> C-a y
List Buffer	C-a b
Paste Buffer	C-a p
Toggle mouse	C-a m
